Steps to install SASS

1. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm)
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   Closed and reopened terminal

2. Installed Node.js version 20.16
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16

3. Installed SASS
   $ npm install sass@3.7.4

4. Verified SASS installation
   $ npx sass --version
